Sentence: High-quality epitaxial thin films of REFeAs(O,F) are required to develop Fe-based super- conducting devices such as Josephson junctions and super- conducting quantum interference devices (SQUIDs) .

Among various phases of iron-based super- conductors, REFeAs(O,F) (RE = rare earth elements, the ZrCuSiAs structure, called '1111') has the highest T c of 55 K with RE = Nd, Sm [2-5] and is the most attractive for potential applications.
